  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Immediately after you hit a creature with a melee attack as part of the Attack action on your turn, you can use a bonus action to attempt to push that target with your horns. The target must be within 5 feet of you and be no more than one size larger than you. Unless it succeeds on a Strength saving throw against a DC equal to 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Strength modifier or Dexterity modifier (You choose this when you select this species), you push it up to 10 feet away from you.<br /></p>",
